 planin Newry earlier today, it was revealed that the association's world council will aim to ultimately earn recognition from the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.984502415234307e-16, \"text\": \"Newry\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newry\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the launch\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"the association's world council\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The end goal is to see Gaelic football, hurling and camogie staged at Olympic Games in the future.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The end goal\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"Gaelic football\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"hurling\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"camogie\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The revelation came as the new strategic plan was unveiled.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The revelation\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"the new strategic plan\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This new plan charts a direction for the ever-growing seven international units and 475 clubs across World GAA.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This new plan\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"a direction\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"the ever-growing seven international units\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"475 clubs\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"World GAA\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan ranges from 2024 to 2026 and features a variety of objectives to realise the GAA's vision as a sustainable community-based and volunteer-led association.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 666, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9972562948153507, \"rank\": 0.0027512537058926594, \"text\": \"GAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The plan\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"objectives\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"a sustainable community-based and volunteer-led association\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Based on last year's figures, approximately 64,000 Irish people are expected to leave these shores this year by the month of April.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"last year's figures\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"these shores\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This exodus has seen World GAA grow at an enormous rate.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This exodus\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"World GAA\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"an enormous rate\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To reflect this trend, four strategic themes were identified to form the core of the GAA's operational plan across the globe for the next three years.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9972562948153507, \"rank\": 0.0027512537058926594, \"text\": \"GAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this trend\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"four strategic themes\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the core\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"the next three years\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These include coaching and games, health and well-being, PR and communications and officer training.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaching\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"well-being\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"PR\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"communications\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"officer training\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Networking and securing recognition with local sporting federations through officer training and PR are key pillars that will be used to help gain international recognition for the GAA from 60 sporting federations across the world.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9972562948153507, \"rank\": 0.0027512537058926594, \"text\": \"GAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaelic_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"local sporting federations\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"officer training\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"PR\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"key pillars\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"international recognition\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"60 sporting federations\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The association's strategy centres on countries in each unit of World GAA firstly seeking national sport recognition from their respective federations.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The association's strategy centres\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"each unit\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"World GAA\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"national sport recognition\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective federations\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each GAA council will then establish a work group to identify the number of countries in their unit, the number of clubs in each country, and then target to meet with consulates to understand the process of eligibility for Olympic participation and connect with sporting and government departments.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each GAA council\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"a work group\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"their unit\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"clubs\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"each country\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"consulates\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"eligibility\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic participation\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting and government departments\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These work groups and connections will be geared towards eventually achieving AIMS (Alliance of Independent recognised Members of Sports) recognition.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\", \"score\": 0.9986725125809094, \"rank\": 0.0013292518434228242, \"text\": \"AIMS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These work groups\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"connections\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"Alliance\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"Independent\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The target is to establish AIMS recognition by 2026 and to re-assess the situation at that stage.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\", \"score\": 0.9986725125809094, \"rank\": 0.0013292518434228242, \"text\": \"AIMS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_International_Marathons_and_Distance_Races\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The target\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaelic football and hurling previously made a brief appearance in the 1904 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gaelic football\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"a brief appearance\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1904 Olympics\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sports featured in an unofficial capacity when Fenians FC from Chicago beat host team St Louis by 10 goals to nil.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Republican_Brotherhood\", \"score\": 0.9227324094965018, \"rank\": 0.08373750102362852, \"text\": \"Fenians\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Republican_Brotherhood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Republican_Brotherhood\"}, {\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9999788368502118, \"rank\": 2.106552665181329e-05, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}], \"noun_phrases\":